name: Hungry Dinosaurs
overview: Eat or be eaten! Get ready because war has been declared in the mightiest and most magnificent action puzzle the world has ever seen! Hungry Dinosaurs are monsters that just love eating. here they compete to see just how many tasty eggs they can eat. It's the heroic battle world of "eat or be eaten". Take part in the mightiest action puzzle game the world has ever seen, and see if you can survive! Stand up against the speedy and powerful attack of the Dinosaurs, the ultra-strong characters, and fight them with your sure-death technique. Will it be you who wins? Or....?
